TEXT.S: Haji Hassanal Bolkiah Mu'izzaddin Waddaulah 7 bulad 15 demiad, Haji Hassanal Bolkiah Mu'izzaddin Waddaulah, u misingkiway. 1946 a mihca nalecuhan) u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Brunei ayza sa ci Haji Hassanal Bolkiah Mu'izzaddin Waddaulah, micakat a demiad sa i 1967 a mihca 10 bulad 5 demiad.
